### Create Workspace
POST http://localhost:5000/workspace-api/workspaces
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZjhjOWJhYmY1NzU0YjQ5MjJiODVkNCIsImVtYWlsIjoidXNlcjFAbWFpbC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiVVNFUiIsImlhdCI6MTc3NzkxMjgxMywiZXhwIjoxNzc3OTk5MjEzfQ.7T8vi-p-S3MKqBzshJ1bGeUTEh-2p_RN5zm1HEXPoLE

{
  "workspaceName": "Team Workspace",
  "description": "Main workspace for team communication"
}


